        <Parent_String>ceremonial chairs [300133851], chairs by function [300038131], chairs (furniture forms) [300037772], single seating furniture [300037771], seating furniture [300037769], furniture by form or function [300048628], furniture [300037680], furnishings by form or function [300037342], furnishings (works) [300037336], Furnishings (hierarchy name) [300037335], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
